rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0004
rows.name: [ST:wide ]—He was killed in action by enemy fire.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0006
rows.name: Lieutenant, when we find the Central Life...[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0007
rows.name:
Let's prepare the latest B.B. model for Marcus
first thing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0008
rows.name:
That's right!
A B.B. more handsome than Gwin-san![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0009
rows.name:
And while we're at it, tall and
slim but muscular would be good-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0011
rows.name:
Taller than Gwin-san, and
a slim-muscular one too, let's prepare that-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0013
rows.name: You two, that's just plain insulting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0015
rows.name:
Let's get him the latest B.B. model that's
more handsome and taller than Gwin![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0017
rows.name: Colonel Elma, they really did a number on us, didn't they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0018
rows.name: But isn't that supposed to be like a god statue to them?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0019
rows.name: Just because one or two god statues were taken...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0020
rows.name: If only it were that simple...[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0022
rows.name:
Anyway, whatever the Growth's objective was,
it doesn't matter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0023
rows.name:
Our mission was to defend NLA.
And that was accomplished.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0027
rows.name:
Well then, shall we all go report
to Commander Vandham together?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0029
rows.name:
Sorry, but could you and Gwin
go on ahead, Irina?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0030
rows.name: I'm concerned about the state of the hangar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140150_MSG0032
rows.name:
Then we'll go report on the mission.
Excuse us.[ST:wait ]
